filename = "segment.zip"

with open(filename, 'r') as f:
    content = "\n" + f.read()
    n_attr = content.count("@attribute")
    content = sub(r'@attribute (\w+).*\n', r'\1,', content, count=n_attr-1)
    content = sub(r'@attribute (\w+).*', r'\1', content)
    content = sub(r'@.*\n', "", content)
    open("data.csv", 'w').write(content)
    
df = pd.read_csv("data.csv", sep=",")

pca = PCA()
table_pca = pca.fit_transform(df.drop("Class",axis=1), df["Class"])

k = 1
for i in np.cumsum(pca.explained_variance_ratio_):
  if i >= 0.95:
    break
  k+=1
title = HTML("<h1> {}  </h1>". format(k))
display(title)

#Kaiser test - eigvals >=1
eigvals, eigvecs = nl.eig(df.corr)
amt = 0
for i in eigvals:
    if i>=1:
      amt+=1
title = HTML("<h1>   - {}  </h1>". format(amt))
display(title)
